{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_07_01",
  "title": "天動瑠依 1話 差を埋める方法",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、{user}さん\nあの、話というのは……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work today‚ {user}-san.\nUm‚ about what you wanted to talk about…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7471026527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "忙しいところすまない\n次回のライブバトルについてなんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry to bother you while you’re busy.\nIt’s about the next live battle…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.6893199761
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "……ランキング五位のグループとの対決を\n断った件……ですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…About how we turned down\nThe match against the fifth-ranked group… right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "え？　あ、ああ……。よく分かったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Oh‚ yeah… How did you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.2736059029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.6095242023
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "最初に断ったあの時……\nちょっと、不思議だったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we first turned it down…\nIt was a little… strange.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.6095242023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.3125175952
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、特に理由も聞かないで\n「そうか」としか言わなかったので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ you didn’t even ask why‚\nAnd you just said‚ “Okay.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.0955785273
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……あれは正直、面を食らってしまってな\nどう答えたものやらって思ってさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… Honestly‚ I was caught off guard‚\nAnd I didM3:Q15w what to say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "三人が決めたことなら……と一度は納得したが\nやっぱり、ちゃんと理由は聞いておきたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I accepted it at first‚ thinking… “If that’s what you three decided…”\nBut I still want to hear your reason properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.0666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.5494808989
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "そうでしたか\n……あの、それぐらい意外でしたか？　断ったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see.\n…Um‚ was it that unexpected? That we declined?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.7666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、瑠依達なら挑戦すると思っていたからな\n断った時の気持ちは、今も変わらないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ yeah‚ I thought you’d challenge them‚ Rui.\nDo you still feel the same way as when you turned it down?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.0666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.4442429063
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "はい、変わりません\nランキング五位には、まだ挑戦しません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ it hasn’t changed.\nWe won’t challenge the fifth-ranked group yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.8666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.2809095062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが挑戦を勧めてくれた理由は\n凄く理解出来ます。……けど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand why {user}-san recommended that we\nchallenge them…But",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.3666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "明らかな時期尚早だと思っています\nバトルのベストスコアで、私達は負けていますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it’s clearly too early.\nWe’re losing in terms of best battle scores‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.2333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.5085740722
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "確かに……でも、だからこその挑戦だと思うんだ\n下剋上を成し遂げんとする挑戦だって――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s true… But that’s why I think it’s a good challenge.\nIt’s a challenge to overcome the odds――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.8000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.2853525158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、なおのことです\n私達は、絶対に勝たないといけないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then all the more reason.\nWe have to win‚ no matter what.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.3000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.9484587983
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "確実に勝てる段階まで、成長する必要がある\n……私達はもう、負ける訳にはいかないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We need to grow until we can definitely win.\n…We can’t afford to lose anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.9484587983,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "負けないためにも\n今は地力をしっかりつけるべきだと私は思っています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So in order not to lose‚\nI believe we should focus on building our foundation right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.6333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.1617218967
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった。瑠依がそう言うのなら、尊重しよう\n功を急いでも結果が伴うとは限らないしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okay. If that’s what you say‚ Rui‚ I’ll respect your decision.\nRushing things doesn’t always lead to good results.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.4333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "理解していただけて嬉しいです\nあの、お話は以上でしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m glad you understand.\nUm‚ is that all?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.9000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.009907722
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "この後、優達と自主練をする予定で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re scheduled to have practice with Yu and Sumire later…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.009907722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、ごめん。それじゃあ最後に……\nこれを渡しておくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ sorry. Then‚ lastly…\nI’ll give you this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.9000017802,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4402.1576091000015,
          "startTime": 131.7333351135
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.7246295607
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "ライブのチケット……？\nこれ、ランキング五位のグループの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A live ticket…?\nThis is… for the fifth-ranked group…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.0666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "挑戦する、しないにかかわらず\n一度、生で観ておくといい。特に、今の瑠依は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whether you challenge them or not‚\nIt’d be good to see them live once. Especially for you right now‚ Rui.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.0333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.7651282624
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "今の私は……ですか？　分かりました\nでも確かに、勉強になりそうですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me right now…? Okay.\nBut it’ll definitely be a learning experience.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.3000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_01-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\nしっかり観ておこうと思います",
      "translations": {
